Government of Maharashtra
Department of Law and Justice
Government Circular No.CHA-2015 / P.No.87 / Q.9
Madam Kama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,
Mantralaya, Mumbai 400 032.
Date - February 14, 2025.
Reference: - Department of Law & Justice, Government Circular, Serial No. 16.01.2025
Circular

The Commissioner of Charities, Deputy Commissioner of Charities on Establishment, Maharashtra State, Mumbai, fixes the seniority number and date of seniority of Group-A cadre officers. Temporary Service Excellence List dated 01.01.2025, Reference No. 1 was published by the Government Circular here. The objections received as on date 08.02.2025 in pursuance of this tentative Service Excellence List are being processed and the present Service Excellence List is being finalised. This final merit list is mentioned in Annexure-A to this circular.
2. The Service Excellence List. The Maharashtra Administrative Tribunal, Bench filed the original application No. In 155/2024. is being published, subject to the final order of the Tribunal.

3. A copy of this Final Service Excellence List is being brought to the notice of all officers of the Charity Deputy Commissioner cadre at the establishment of the Charity Commissioner, Maharashtra State, Mumbai.

Dr. Government Circular A7 of the Government of Maharashtra. The 11019510119.200.110 has been made available on the website with the code 202502141522290212. The circular is being digitally signed and authenticated.
